long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
LC Live Contest Rankings Tracker is a must-have Chrome extension for competitive programmers participating in live coding contests. Stay ahead of the competition with real-time updates on ongoing contests, effortlessly add and monitor friends, and track their progress instantly. Key features include:

Live Contest Tracking: Get instant updates on ongoing coding contests to ensure you never miss a beat.
Friend Monitoring: Add friends with ease and keep track of their rankings and submissions in real-time.
Interactive User Interface: Enjoy a user-friendly interface designed for seamless navigation and ease of use.
Personalized Experience: Customize your tracking preferences and optimize your contest experience.
Enhance your competitive coding journey with LC Live Contest Rankings Tracker. Install now and elevate your contest tracking experience to the next level!
